{"title":"垦荒者之歌","authors":["周彼"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"垦荒者之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周彼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起铁镐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰落满天星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辟开顽石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山飞舞百灵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垦荒者的笑颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映红枯木岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过坳、上崠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿路洒下蜜似的深情；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点滴滴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润了荒山的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久眠的荒山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁开褐色的眼睛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖落一身衰草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎主人的来临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我俩永远在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带着一颗诚挚的心来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和荒山结下深厚的友谊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨雪霜拆不散我俩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨难愈多愈亲密。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为它斩除荆棘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它为我扫尽娇气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一丘新垦的梯田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡漾着我俩的欢欣、得意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在无语的交往中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我俩订下神圣的默契；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不吝惜白银似的汗珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它决不吝惜黄金谷粒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将忠实于我的诺言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远和它生活在一起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每个收获季节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向党献上一份厚礼。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}